tests.name: PlaceOrderComponent should match the 3 drinks from DrinkService
PlaceOrderComponent should increment the drink amount on increment
PlaceOrderComponent should decrement the drink amount on decrement
PlaceOrderComponent should go below 0 on decrement
PlaceOrderComponent should retrieve the calculate the total price
PlaceOrderComponent should not disable submit button if there are no drinks selected yet
PlaceOrderComponent should enable submit button once drinks are selected
PlaceOrderComponent should navigate to next page on submit
PlaceOrderComponent should filter out un-ordered drinks on submit
PlaceOrderComponent on constructor should set order, numberOfDrinks and ageCheck properties
PlaceOrderComponent on constructor should navigate back if there is no order
PlaceOrderComponent submit should allow if ageCheck is disabled
PlaceOrderComponent submit should allow if user is 24
PlaceOrderComponent submit should not allow if user is 12
PlaceOrderComponent submit should not allow if user is 17
PlaceOrderComponent submit should allow if user is 18
PlaceOrderComponent cancel should navigate back
Test route config should test routeProvider
OrderService test when I use OrderService should retrieve given order
OrderService test when I use OrderService should retrieve from localStorage if local copy does not exist
OrderService test when I use OrderService should clear the localStorage
OrderService test when I use OrderService should not use localStorage when _currentOrder is defined
SuccessComponent should be constructed
SuccessComponent should calculate numberOfDrinks when constructed
